write_up: Bleakness is standard for drill, but Lil Durk has found his own melodic corner of it. ‘Neighorhood Hero’ has some really great lines on it. His later unprecedented popular music success is the result of years and years of hard work, as well as some help from innovations his city neighbor Keef made back in the day.
lyric: Don’t get shot in my areas, ain’t no trauma unit
